<div class="summary"><span>摘要：</span>备受关注的广东省揭阳市原市委书记陈弘平涉嫌受贿、贪污、行贿一案，在佛山中院一审公开开庭审理。</div>
<div class="content">
<p class="img"><img src="http://news.huaxi100.com/uploadfile/2015/0422/20150422080822555.jpg" width="510"></p>
<div  class="main-inner-ad"><script type="text/javascript">
    /*250*250 创建于 2014-12-24*/
    var cpro_id = "u1875634";
